body:
I am trying a simple, immediate SVA in Icarus (main/devel). I get syntax error on the code below. Is immediate assert easy enough to add support for? Also how do I enhance the error if I wish to?

Thanks

```log
t.sv:7: syntax error
t.sv:7: error: Malformed statement
```

```verilog
module m;

  reg [7:0] a;

  initial begin
    #100;
    a1 : assert (!$isunknown(a));
    #10;
    $finish(2);
  end
endmodule : m
```

